item.title: Creating A Project
item.description: Here you will learn how to create a new project on APIToolkit, even if you’re a complete beginner who doesn’t have an APIToolkit account, this article will get you to the point where you create your project and have everything in place with your dashboard all ready for an integration.

item.title: Generating API Keys
item.description: API keys are unique identifiers that are used to authenticate user’s identity. The API key is a crucial component of integrating APIs into your programs. Your uniqueness and distinctiveness as a developer are determined by this factor.
